gAdds a user to your Quick X friends list.

   Press w<rAw>g.
   Enter a slot number.
   Enter a Username.

Now, you can send eXpress messages to this user by pressing the user's
quick-x number, instead of typing the user's name out.

Also, the quick X number of the user will appear in his/her flags column 
in the w<rww>gholist.
